title: Annihilators (Trade Paperback)
description: Gladiator, Quasar, Beta Ray Bill, Ronan the Accuser and the Silver Surfer are the universe’s most powerful squad of first responders: the Annihilators! When this newly formed group receives strange signals from the Dark Nebula — home of the noble race of Spaceknights — these mighty allies set off to investigate. There, they find a blast from the past who has discovered a way to rip a hole through space and time, unleashing the vicious Dire Wraiths! Plus: After the Guardians of the Galaxy disbanded, Rocket Raccoon settled into a quiet life with a steady job in a mailroom. But when a killer clown made of sentient wood attacks him at work, the trigger-fingered and quick-witted hero must journey to Planet X — home of his old buddy Groot, the giant tree-creature — in search of answers! Collecting ANNIHILATORS #1-4
